overview: Hosted by the Award-winning "Queen of Clean" Chonda Pierce, THOU SHALT LAUGH 5 presents returning fan favorites Bone Hampton, Gilbert Esquivel, Taylor Mason and the hilariously funny Joey I.L.O., Leland Klassen, and Daren Streblow. Filmed live in Nashville, Tennessee - THOU SHALT LAUGH 5 is, without a doubt, the fifth best THOU SHALT LAUGH ever! Wait, that didn't come out right...
title: Thou Shalt Laugh 5
